<h2>Residential</h2>
The windows are often used for enclosed patios, sunrooms, and serving windows between kitchens and dining rooms in residential settings. All residential folding glass walls are constructed out of sturdy aluminum. This allows for a durable frame that will not warp, rot, or need constant finish¬†maintenance. There are several screening options available to keep out unwanted pests, while still allowing guests to enjoy the natural environment.

