<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37022" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/fgwindows-restaurant.png" alt="" width="680" height="400" />
<h2>Commercial</h2>
Commercial applications include restaurant windows, hotel windows, and stadium boxes. Open up a restaurant to patio seating or pass food through the folding glass windows from the kitchen. An all aluminum frame makes the folding glass windows suitable for hospital or retirement home facilities.¬† One of several ADA compliant sill options can be utilized to meet code requirements in such instances.

